title: Gorgeous 2 bed 1 bath
app_fee: $50.00 money order per applicant 18 years or older
posting_body: ['Look no further!', 'We offer a great 2 bed 1 bath apartment in the heart of Highland Park.', 'Great complex well kept.', 'Plenty of counter top and storage space.', ' Friendly neighborhood right off York and Ave 56.', 'Lots of shops, Restaurants and activities in the neighborhood.', 'Grocery stores within walking distance', 'Parks-Playground-pool-Basketball courts-skate park-running track/exercise equipment.', 'Elementary, Middle, & High schools near.', 'Plus minutes from 110, 2, 134, and 5 Freeways!!', 'Ready to move in 8/15/22', 'Apartment Amenities:', '-2 Parking spaces', '-UTILITIES INCLUDED: water and trash', '-Stove and Garbage Disposal', '-Air Conditioner', '- New Paint', '-Wood-like Flooring', '-On site Laundry', '- RENT=$1,800', '-Deposit starting at $1,800 on approve credit', 'Community Features', '• Well kept', '• Quiet neighborhood', '• Your local shopping stores near you', 'We pay for WATER & TRASH!', 'CALL TODAY', 'show contact info', 'for more information or to SCHEDULE A TOUR!', '5618 Meridian St', 'Los Angeles, CA 90042', 'show contact info', '**Come prepared**', 'Must be 18+ to apply', '$50 Money Order for each application', 'Copy of California DL/ID', 'Copy of Social Security Card', 'Proof of income (paystubs, bank statements and/or Taxes)', 'In order to qualify you need to make 2.5x the rent', 'NO Evictions or balances with Utility Companies.']
